I first made this when it came out in the magazine and loved it. I have made it multiple times since to rave reviews. Including last night - where my friends asked for the recipe...so I sent them to Epicurious! Wax beans are difficult to find so I often substitute green beans, but aside from that I do not make substitutions. I agree with other reviewer - do not be afraid of the anchovies - they blend beautifully.

