This is the ultimate summer grilling and entertaining dish, and a great way to make use of the fresh Farmer's market ingredients. Easy and so beautiful to serve. Was hesitant at first because of the anchovies, but do not fear. They blend wonderfully with the rest of the dish. Don't pass this one up.

